{"tid":1198772,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】新假期推介港豬去添馬公園野餐！","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T11:55:43.000Z","uid":79382,"like":143,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8f068b1b3b136e6a71d0491043f14d74ee281a09","tid":1198772,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:20:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/218904028237369/posts/2147970905330662?s=711566308&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F218904028237369%2Fposts%2F2147970905330662%3Fs%3D711566308%26sfns%3Dmo&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCCHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=4f3f389f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/218904028237369/posts/2147970905330662?s=711566308&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQ6Su9C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQ6Su9C.png&h=168d1e34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110bb9e4c927ace8552d686593e469010c8403aa","tid":1198772,"uid":203251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b63372c86837d58e936527d17ed7c2ded17d17c","tid":1198772,"uid":36478,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d2b1a6f972e418b1b7bdda644d8473a3ad2d21","tid":1198772,"uid":67348,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"政府總部附近嘅添馬公園一直係熱門嘅野餐好去處。位於金鐘嘅添馬公園佔地17,000平方米，交通便捷，金鐘港鐵站一出，過條天橋就到，喺咁擠迫繁忙嘅金鐘竟然有咁大片草地，仲有無敵海景，簡直就係城市中的綠洲。平時公園嘅草地出晒名只作觀賞用途，但添馬公園喺正政府總部隔籬，仲有行政長官辦公室同立法會綜合大樓，草地都可以任踩唔嬲，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家要好好利用呢片草地先得，除咗野餐，大家仲諗唔諗到可以做啲咩呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13898892d7323676f7c932ecae3775265fa19faa","tid":1198772,"uid":213819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:26:35.000Z","msg":"未去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />約下朋友仔先"},{"pid":"2d8394c28f98ab6cfa56364ab373ace02ba7e294","tid":1198772,"uid":78039,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:27:19.000Z","msg":"上大陸網介紹埋比大陸人仲開心"},{"pid":"128b78d0d64df69d19039b2b1e5db800ed04503c","tid":1198772,"uid":38988,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:30:48.000Z","msg":"呢個編輯叻仔"},{"pid":"9378dfa989ddba9d5778ff88ba6cd9e9d03ba7dc","tid":1198772,"uid":19557,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1428ef5d982182a183fa3cd2d7cae391ae1770f","tid":1198772,"uid":53349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢幾日天氣好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8bc2b65b4c4f1e0fc582f4c4d6dfd6ed0a3938","tid":1198772,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:09:53.000Z","msg":"介紹比啲支那西"},{"pid":"baa64a1737449adfe1e0dd4a61004a334631c4bd","tid":1198772,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:18:02.000Z","msg":"呢幾日天氣好喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fdb4587ebf6425b